<tr class="field-options asset-styles">
	<td></td>
	<td colspan="4">
	
		<h3>Grafik-Größen</h3>
		
		<p>Die Schlüssel müssen gültige Ruby-Variablenname sein (z.B. <code>sidebar_thumb</code>), die Größen gültige <a href="http://www.imagemagick.org/script/command-line-processing.php#geometry">ImageMagick-Formate</a> (z.B. <code>150x100</code>).</p>
		
		<ul class="clearfix">
		<% styles = defined?(field) ? field.styles : Array.new(3) %>
		<% for style in styles %>
			
			<% if style.is_a?(Hash) %>
				<% key_s   = style[:key] %>
				<% style_s = style[:style] %>
			<% else %>
				<% key_s = style_s = '' %>
			<% end %>
			
			<li>
				<p><label>
					<span>Schlüssel:</span>
					<input type="text" name="category[fields][][asset_styles][][key]" value="<%=h key_s %>" />
				</label></p>
				<p><label>
					<span>Größe:</span>
					<input type="text" name="category[fields][][asset_styles][][style]" value="<%=h style_s %>" />
				</label></p>
			</li>
		<% end %>
		</ul>
		
		<p><a href="javascript:void(0)" class="smaller button invert add-asset-style">Größe hinzufügen</a></p>
		
	</td>
</tr>